{"tid":1331010,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"政府依家好撚急，係咁搞啲大單嘢同嘗試喺連燈帶風","createTime":"2019-07-18T19:19:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-18T19:57:31.000Z","uid":52023,"like":50,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"b3337a6c7f14e82ebeaa51738a7b8034ae93a2d6","tid":1331010,"uid":52023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T19:19:25.000Z","msg":"又搞720遊行<br />\n中資又派假俾啲濕鳩遊行<br />\n又高調多次CALL成車人搞啲連燶<br />\n周圍散播白色恐怖捉咗幾多人會告幾多人<br />\n連續幾晚喺連燈嘗試分化搞破壞<br />\n但係全部都唔成功<br />\n再搞都唔會成功<br />\n因為依家急嘅係政府 唔係我哋<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>政府再一次幫大家證明<br />\n乜嘢連燶 登報 聯署 搵外國勢力 文宣攻勢 <br />\n大家所有做嘅嘢都係方向正確<br />\n各自爬山係冇做錯到嘅</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7458c494ed50f3b29d80179e113f9231f1f22c4","tid":1331010,"uid":180429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T19:20:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9692443365a30c22da1e7d5c124a8c7185ec1b1e","tid":1331010,"uid":262674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b3337a6c7f14e82ebeaa51738a7b8034ae93a2d6","tid":1331010,"uid":52023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T19:19:25.000Z","msg":"又搞720遊行<br />\n中資又派假俾啲濕鳩遊行<br />\n又高調多次CALL成車人搞啲連燶<br />\n周圍散播白色恐怖捉咗幾多人會告幾多人<br />\n連續幾晚喺連燈嘗試分化搞破壞<br />\n但係全部都唔成功<br />\n再搞都唔會成功<br />\n因為依家急嘅係政府 唔係我哋<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>政府再一